### Get all products
GET https://localhost:7000/api/products?page=1&pageSize=10

### Get product by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/api/products/1

### Create a new product
POST https://localhost:7000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Product",
  "description": "A brand new product",
  "price": 49.99
}

### Update an existing product
PUT https://localhost:7000/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "description": "An updated product description",
  "price": 59.99
}

### Delete a product
DELETE https://localhost:7000/api/products/1

### Test validation - invalid product (empty name)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "description": "This should fail validation",
  "price": -10
}